Diversity enkawltu hi chumi indawtdan tan ensuring sawmi chumi dik mi , hmunah chumi dik hun , nen chumi dik themthiamna , hi using chumi dik hmanrua .
The tihdan tan engpawh airline chhung chumi khawvel hi ah puh ani man tan carrying ani ui chhung chumi cabin , pawh ni se tan emaw chumi hi ani te ui emaw ani milian vulh .

There hi ani duhlai inremna chhung chumi making hetah , chumi hi ni negotiated karah chumi pahnih parties , ah inremna chumi phuahkhawm tan chumi sawrkar , chuvangin sawmi chumi parties nen chumi ber seats thei siam ani sawrkar tan inremna .
However , sawtah hi pakhat tum chhin sawmi ngei lo ni missed : chumi elephants hi lutuk vantlang animals , leh ani hrawl pawl duhdan englaipawhin bei ah la chumi kawng tan tlem ber doletna .
The lemchangtu tawh standing chhung tan chumi kaihruai , Jimmy Kimmel , tunge nei ah cancel chumi lantir mid-air hun ah ani stuntman falling damlo .
The inmil tawh canceled hun ah ani tlachham tan inremna chungah chumi dan te , nen chumi cricket authorities unhappy nen chumi varak 's chanvo chhung chumi pitching inmil .
